p.value: Open to researchers. Appointments are necessary for the use of manuscript and archival collections.

Published citations should take the following form:
                <lb/>
                <lb/> Identification of item, date (if known); Fales Library Events Video Collection; MSS 307; box number; folder number; Fales Library and Special Collections, New York University Libraries.

The Fales Library Events Video Collection contains video and audio of events either arranged by or held at the Fales Library relating to the Fales Library, Fales archival collections and/or the Fales Food Studies Series.
This collection contains video and audio of events either arranged by or held at Fales Library.
